# This directory holds real-world PDF files for integration testing.
# PDFs are intentionally excluded from git (see .gitignore).
# Add your own PDFs here locally — they will never be committed.
#
# Recommended corpus structure:
#   corpus/
#     born-digital/       PDFs created by software (Word, LaTeX, etc.)
#     scanned/            Scanned documents with image pages
#     forms/              PDFs with AcroForm fields
#     encrypted/          Password-protected PDFs (include passwords in a local notes file)
#     malformed/          PDFs that violate the spec — for robustness testing
#     large/              Large PDFs (100+ pages, 50MB+) — for streaming tests
#     medical/            (gitignored separately) — real patient documents, NEVER commit
